    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 10th level, you can use your action to increase your powers of perception. When you do so, choose one of the following benefits, which lasts until you are &amp;Reference[condition=incapacitated] or you take a short or long rest. You can't use the feature again until you finish a rest.</p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Darkvision\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Darkvision</span></h3> <p>You gain &amp;Reference[rule=darkvision] out to a range of 60 feet.</p></div><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Ethereal Sight\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"2\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Ethereal Sight</span></h3> <p>You can see into the Ethereal Plane within 60 feet of you.</p></div><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Greater Comprehension\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Greater Comprehension</span></h3> <p>You can read any language.</p></div><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"See Invisibility\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"4\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">See Invisibility</span></h3> <p>You can see &amp;Reference[condition=invisible] creatures and objects within 10 feet of you that are within line of sight.</p></div></div></div>",
